Author: Tercioo &lt;terciob19@hotmail.com&gt;
Date:   Sat Apr 13 13:00:51 2019 -0300

    Moving rank text to a new Statusbar in the Player Detail Window

    Rank information was shown in the header above the tabs, now the player details window has a statusbar and the rank information is shown there." />



                <TextBlock Text="Current Download" Style="{StaticResource DetailSubTitleStyle}" Margin="{StaticResource SmallTopMargin}" />
                <TextBlock Style="{StaticResource DetailBodyStyle}" Text="{x:Bind MasterMenuItem.CurrentDownload, Mode=OneWay}" />

                <TextBlock Text="Suggested Download" Style="{StaticResource DetailSubTitleStyle}" Margin="{StaticResource SmallTopMargin}" />
                <TextBlock Style="{StaticResource DetailBodyStyle}" Margin="{StaticResource MediumBottomMargin}" Text="{x:Bind MasterMenuItem.SuggestedDownload, Mode=OneWay}" />
            </StackPanel>

        </StackPanel>
    </ScrollViewer>
</UserControl>



